{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1120,"text":"\"These are the times,\""},{"time":3440,"text":"said Thomas Paine,"},{"time":5480,"text":"\"that try men's souls.\""},{"time":8160,"text":"And they're trying ours now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9640,"text":"This is a fateful moment\nin the history of the West."},{"time":13840,"text":"We've seen divisive elections\nand divided societies."},{"time":19360,"text":"We've seen a growth of extremism"},{"time":21920,"text":"in politics and religion,"},{"time":24720,"text":"all of it fueled by anxiety,\nuncertainty and fear,"},{"time":29160,"text":"of a world that's changing\nalmost faster than we can bear,"},{"time":34480,"text":"and the sure knowledge\nthat it's going to change faster still."},{"time":39440,"text":"I have a friend in Washington."},{"time":40920,"text":"I asked him, what was it like\nbeing in America"},{"time":43120,"text":"during the recent presidential election?"},{"time":46880,"text":"He said to me, \"Well,"},{"time":48880,"text":"it was like the man"},{"time":51680,"text":"sitting on the deck of the Titanic"},{"time":54720,"text":"with a glass of whiskey in his hand"},{"time":58320,"text":"and he's saying,\n'I know I asked for ice --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":62120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":67680,"text":"but this is ridiculous.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":71560,"text":"So is there something we can do,"},{"time":75000,"text":"each of us,"},{"time":77360,"text":"to be able to face\nthe future without fear?"},{"time":80240,"text":"I think there is."},{"time":82800,"text":"And one way into it is to see"},{"time":85000,"text":"that perhaps the most simple way\ninto a culture and into an age"},{"time":90920,"text":"is to ask: What do people worship?"},{"time":93920,"text":"People have worshipped\nso many different things --"},{"time":96440,"text":"the sun, the stars, the storm."},{"time":98840,"text":"Some people worship many gods,\nsome one, some none."},{"time":102840,"text":"In the 19th and 20th centuries,"},{"time":105720,"text":"people worshipped the nation,"},{"time":107920,"text":"the Aryan race, the communist state."},{"time":110400,"text":"What do we worship?"},{"time":113440,"text":"I think future anthropologists"},{"time":116400,"text":"will take a look at the books we read"},{"time":119320,"text":"on self-help, self-realization,"},{"time":122440,"text":"self-esteem."},{"time":124400,"text":"They'll look at the way\nwe talk about morality"},{"time":127240,"text":"as being true to oneself,"},{"time":129440,"text":"the way we talk about politics"},{"time":131880,"text":"as a matter of individual rights,"},{"time":134680,"text":"and they'll look at this wonderful\nnew religious ritual we have created."},{"time":140040,"text":"You know the one?"},{"time":141840,"text":"Called the \"selfie.\""},{"time":144440,"text":"And I think they'll conclude\nthat what we worship in our time"},{"time":148080,"text":"is the self, the me, the I."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151680,"text":"And this is great."},{"time":153600,"text":"It's liberating.\nIt's empowering. It's wonderful."},{"time":157520,"text":"But don't forget that biologically,\nwe're social animals."},{"time":163200,"text":"We've spent most\nof our evolutionary history"},{"time":166840,"text":"in small groups."},{"time":168720,"text":"We need those face-to-face interactions"},{"time":172440,"text":"where we learn\nthe choreography of altruism"},{"time":176880,"text":"and where we create those spiritual goods"},{"time":179960,"text":"like friendship and trust\nand loyalty and love"},{"time":184200,"text":"that redeem our solitude."},{"time":187560,"text":"When we have too much of the \"I\"\nand too little of the \"we,\""},{"time":191520,"text":"we can find ourselves vulnerable,"},{"time":194400,"text":"fearful and alone."},{"time":197080,"text":"It was no accident\nthat Sherry Turkle of MIT"},{"time":200080,"text":"called the book she wrote\non the impact of social media"},{"time":203200,"text":"\"Alone Together.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":206400,"text":"So I think the simplest way\nof safeguarding the future \"you\""},{"time":211440,"text":"is to strengthen the future \"us\""},{"time":214520,"text":"in three dimensions:"},{"time":215800,"text":"the us of relationship,"},{"time":217840,"text":"the us of identity"},{"time":220120,"text":"and the us of responsibility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221880,"text":"So let me first\ntake the us of relationship."},{"time":224480,"text":"And here, forgive me if I get personal."},{"time":227400,"text":"Once upon a time,"},{"time":229800,"text":"a very long time ago,"},{"time":232280,"text":"I was a 20-year-old undergraduate"},{"time":234960,"text":"studying philosophy."},{"time":236640,"text":"I was into Nietzsche and Schopenhauer\nand Sartre and Camus."},{"time":240520,"text":"I was full of ontological uncertainty"},{"time":244920,"text":"and existential angst."},{"time":246480,"text":"It was terrific."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250080,"text":"I was self-obsessed\nand thoroughly unpleasant to know,"},{"time":253320,"text":"until one day I saw"},{"time":255920,"text":"across the courtyard"},{"time":258079,"text":"a girl"},{"time":259480,"text":"who was everything that I wasn't."},{"time":263080,"text":"She radiated sunshine."},{"time":265120,"text":"She emanated joy."},{"time":268680,"text":"I found out her name was Elaine."},{"time":270600,"text":"We met. We talked."},{"time":272080,"text":"We married."},{"time":273520,"text":"And 47 years, three children\nand eight grandchildren later,"},{"time":277880,"text":"I can safely say"},{"time":279440,"text":"it was the best decision\nI ever took in my life,"},{"time":282400,"text":"because it's the people not like us"},{"time":286040,"text":"that make us grow."},{"time":288400,"text":"And that is why I think"},{"time":291440,"text":"we have to do just that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294040,"text":"The trouble with Google filters,"},{"time":296160,"text":"Facebook friends"},{"time":298120,"text":"and reading the news by narrowcasting\nrather than broadcasting"},{"time":301880,"text":"means that we're surrounded\nalmost entirely by people like us"},{"time":306720,"text":"whose views, whose opinions,\nwhose prejudices, even,"},{"time":310240,"text":"are just like ours."},{"time":312200,"text":"And Cass Sunstein of Harvard has shown"},{"time":314920,"text":"that if we surround ourselves\nwith people with the same views as us,"},{"time":319320,"text":"we get more extreme."},{"time":322440,"text":"I think we need to renew\nthose face-to-face encounters"},{"time":326240,"text":"with the people not like us."},{"time":329280,"text":"I think we need to do that"},{"time":331400,"text":"in order to realize\nthat we can disagree strongly"},{"time":335480,"text":"and yet still stay friends."},{"time":338800,"text":"It's in those face-to-face encounters"},{"time":340920,"text":"that we discover\nthat the people not like us"},{"time":344920,"text":"are just people, like us."},{"time":348800,"text":"And actually, every time"},{"time":351640,"text":"we hold out the hand of friendship"},{"time":353960,"text":"to somebody not like us,"},{"time":356000,"text":"whose class or creed\nor color are different from ours,"},{"time":362040,"text":"we heal"},{"time":363760,"text":"one of the fractures"},{"time":365400,"text":"of our wounded world."},{"time":367200,"text":"That is the us of relationship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370120,"text":"Second is the us of identity."},{"time":373400,"text":"Let me give you a thought experiment."},{"time":376240,"text":"Have you been to Washington?\nHave you seen the memorials?"},{"time":378960,"text":"Absolutely fascinating."},{"time":380680,"text":"There's the Lincoln Memorial:"},{"time":382320,"text":"Gettysburg Address on one side,\nSecond Inaugural on the other."},{"time":386760,"text":"You go to the Jefferson Memorial,"},{"time":388520,"text":"screeds of text."},{"time":390480,"text":"Martin Luther King Memorial,"},{"time":392520,"text":"more than a dozen quotes\nfrom his speeches."},{"time":394960,"text":"I didn't realize,\nin America you read memorials."},{"time":399800,"text":"Now go to the equivalent\nin London in Parliament Square"},{"time":403720,"text":"and you will see that the monument\nto David Lloyd George"},{"time":407120,"text":"contains three words:"},{"time":409160,"text":"David Lloyd George."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":413560,"text":"Nelson Mandela gets two."},{"time":415360,"text":"Churchill gets just one:"},{"time":417720,"text":"Churchill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418960,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":420280,"text":"Why the difference?\nI'll tell you why the difference."},{"time":422800,"text":"Because America was from the outset\na nation of wave after wave of immigrants,"},{"time":427120,"text":"so it had to create an identity"},{"time":429320,"text":"which it did by telling a story"},{"time":431680,"text":"which you learned at school,\nyou read on memorials"},{"time":434360,"text":"and you heard repeated\nin presidential inaugural addresses."},{"time":438240,"text":"Britain until recently\nwasn't a nation of immigrants,"},{"time":441320,"text":"so it could take identity for granted."},{"time":443800,"text":"The trouble is now"},{"time":447040,"text":"that two things have happened\nwhich shouldn't have happened together."},{"time":450560,"text":"The first thing is in the West\nwe've stopped telling this story"},{"time":453880,"text":"of who we are and why,"},{"time":455440,"text":"even in America."},{"time":457440,"text":"And at the same time,"},{"time":459040,"text":"immigration is higher\nthan it's ever been before."},{"time":463920,"text":"So when you tell a story\nand your identity is strong,"},{"time":467240,"text":"you can welcome the stranger,"},{"time":469400,"text":"but when you stop telling the story,"},{"time":471920,"text":"your identity gets weak"},{"time":473480,"text":"and you feel threatened by the stranger."},{"time":477000,"text":"And that's bad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478600,"text":"I tell you, Jews have been scattered\nand dispersed and exiled for 2,000 years."},{"time":484920,"text":"We never lost our identity."},{"time":486640,"text":"Why? Because at least once a year,"},{"time":488760,"text":"on the festival of Passover,"},{"time":490520,"text":"we told our story\nand we taught it to our children"},{"time":493480,"text":"and we ate the unleavened\nbread of affliction"},{"time":495760,"text":"and tasted the bitter herbs of slavery."},{"time":498200,"text":"So we never lost our identity."},{"time":500280,"text":"I think collectively"},{"time":502000,"text":"we've got to get back\nto telling our story,"},{"time":504880,"text":"who we are, where we came from,"},{"time":506920,"text":"what ideals by which we live."},{"time":510400,"text":"And if that happens,"},{"time":512280,"text":"we will become strong enough"},{"time":514720,"text":"to welcome the stranger and say,"},{"time":517400,"text":"\"Come and share our lives,"},{"time":520520,"text":"share our stories,"},{"time":522720,"text":"share our aspirations and dreams.\""},{"time":526880,"text":"That is the us of identity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528800,"text":"And finally, the us of responsibility."},{"time":532840,"text":"Do you know something?"},{"time":534120,"text":"My favorite phrase in all of politics,"},{"time":536760,"text":"very American phrase,"},{"time":539520,"text":"is: \"We the people.\""},{"time":543120,"text":"Why \"we the people?\""},{"time":544360,"text":"Because it says that we all\nshare collective responsibility"},{"time":549480,"text":"for our collective future."},{"time":552040,"text":"And that's how things\nreally are and should be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555920,"text":"Have you noticed how magical thinking"},{"time":559280,"text":"has taken over our politics?"},{"time":562840,"text":"So we say, all you've got to do\nis elect this strong leader"},{"time":568680,"text":"and he or she will solve\nall our problems for us."},{"time":574640,"text":"Believe me, that is magical thinking."},{"time":579400,"text":"And then we get the extremes:"},{"time":581000,"text":"the far right, the far left,"},{"time":583920,"text":"the extreme religious\nand the extreme anti-religious,"},{"time":587640,"text":"the far right dreaming\nof a golden age that never was,"},{"time":592600,"text":"the far left dreaming\nof a utopia that never will be"},{"time":597400,"text":"and the religious and anti-religious\nequally convinced"},{"time":601440,"text":"that all it takes is God\nor the absence of God"},{"time":605800,"text":"to save us from ourselves."},{"time":608760,"text":"That, too, is magical thinking,"},{"time":611960,"text":"because the only people\nwho will save us from ourselves"},{"time":616640,"text":"is we the people,"},{"time":619040,"text":"all of us together."},{"time":621240,"text":"And when we do that,"},{"time":624840,"text":"and when we move from the politics of me"},{"time":628240,"text":"to the politics of all of us together,"},{"time":631640,"text":"we rediscover those beautiful,\ncounterintuitive truths:"},{"time":638440,"text":"that a nation is strong"},{"time":640720,"text":"when it cares for the weak,"},{"time":643240,"text":"that it becomes rich"},{"time":645080,"text":"when it cares for the poor,"},{"time":647240,"text":"it becomes invulnerable\nwhen it cares about the vulnerable."},{"time":651880,"text":"That is what makes great nations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654320,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":663120,"text":"So here is my simple suggestion."},{"time":666720,"text":"It might just change your life,"},{"time":670240,"text":"and it might just help\nto begin to change the world."},{"time":674400,"text":"Do a search and replace operation"},{"time":678360,"text":"on the text of your mind,"},{"time":681120,"text":"and wherever you encounter\nthe word \"self,\""},{"time":684240,"text":"substitute the word \"other.\""},{"time":687400,"text":"So instead of self-help, other-help;"},{"time":690680,"text":"instead of self-esteem, other-esteem."},{"time":695240,"text":"And if you do that,"},{"time":697240,"text":"you will begin to feel the power"},{"time":700840,"text":"of what for me is one\nof the most moving sentences"},{"time":704880,"text":"in all of religious literature."},{"time":708120,"text":"\"Though I walk through the valley\nof the shadow of death,"},{"time":713040,"text":"I will fear no evil,"},{"time":715520,"text":"for you are with me.\""},{"time":718400,"text":"We can face any future without fear"},{"time":722960,"text":"so long as we know"},{"time":724720,"text":"we will not face it alone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":728080,"text":"So for the sake of the future \"you,\""},{"time":732160,"text":"together let us strengthen"},{"time":735040,"text":"the future \"us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":737320,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738560,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}